1
00:00:39,020 --> 00:00:40,360
May I be like the stars

2
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,580
and you like the moon.

3
00:00:42,450 --> 00:00:43,670
As long as the world remains,

4
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:45,780
so shall we.

5
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

6
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:06,060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

7
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,370
I want to be with you forever.

8
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

9
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:17,480
You and she are ultimately different.

10
00:01:37,970 --> 00:01:39,600
Have you ever

11
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,789
truly cared for me?

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,250
No.

13
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,360
Never.

14
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:57,720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

15
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,310
May we live and die together,

16
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,040
and share life and death as one.

17
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:45,790
[Moonlight Mystique]

18
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:49,990
[Episode 22]

19
00:02:50,130 --> 00:02:54,340
[Unbridled Pavilion]

20
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,680
Cang Shan!

21
00:03:01,310 --> 00:03:02,400
Cang Shan!

22
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,560
Coming.

23
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,310
Cang Shan!

24
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:05,120
Who is it?

25
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,910
Cang Shan!

26
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,590
Cang Shan!

27
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,910
Cang Shan!

28
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,160
Cang Shan!

29
00:03:14,660 --> 00:03:15,530
[Unbridled Pavilion]

30
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:16,010
Cang…

31
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:17,380
[Mrs. Cang, Demon Race, Stone Clan]

32
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,800
Mother?

33
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,610
I-It's really you.

34
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,090
What brings you here?

35
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,240
Cang Shan,

36
00:03:23,690 --> 00:03:25,620
something's happened to our Stone Clan.

37
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,390
Mother, you came all the way here

38
00:03:28,410 --> 00:03:29,500
and insisted on meeting with Master.

39
00:03:29,530 --> 00:03:31,380
Has something serious happened in the Stone Clan?

40
00:03:32,010 --> 00:03:33,900
Thank you for meeting me, Master Fan.

41
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,590
Recently, the Stone Clan has been in turmoil.

42
00:03:35,620 --> 00:03:36,740
Every night,

43
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:38,820
members of the clan go missing and die.

44
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:40,890
The bodies of the deceased

45
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,160
will be discovered the next day

46
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,630
in the stone forest.

47
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:48,230
The details of their deaths differ,

48
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:50,000
but they share one thing in common:

49
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,470
they all died

50
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:53,020
with their eyes wide open.

51
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:02,290
[Cang Xuan, Demon Race, Chief of the Stone Clan]

52
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,260
No.

53
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,530
I need to go out and investigate.

54
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,360
No!

55
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:07,130
You can't go.

56
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,190
You're the chief.

57
00:04:08,210 --> 00:04:09,330
If something happens to you,

58
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,050
the clan will lose its backbone.

59
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:12,820
Precisely because I'm the chief,

60
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:14,400
I must uncover the truth

61
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,930
and give the clan members an explanation.

62
00:04:15,950 --> 00:04:17,070
Then I'll go with you.

63
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:19,100
No, you stay at home.

64
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,089
What if...

65
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,310
Cang Shan has been away from home for years.

66
00:04:23,220 --> 00:04:24,540
If you leave

67
00:04:24,930 --> 00:04:26,160
and something happens to you,

68
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:28,030
you won't get to see your son

69
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:29,650
ever again.

70
00:04:31,010 --> 00:04:32,560
It's better if he doesn't come back.

71
00:04:33,570 --> 00:04:35,120
The Stone Clan today

72
00:04:35,210 --> 00:04:37,360
is no longer the same as it used to be.

73
00:04:52,690 --> 00:04:54,260
Then did the chief...

74
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,159
He never came back.

75
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:58,060
I led the clan members

76
00:04:58,090 --> 00:04:59,650
to search every corner

77
00:04:59,670 --> 00:05:00,550
of the Stone Clan,

78
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,510
but there was no trace of him.

79
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:03,660
Mother.

80
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:06,720
I'll go back with you to search for him.

81
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,400
I've always been straightforward.

82
00:05:10,570 --> 00:05:11,570
In terms of spiritual power,

83
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,750
only Master Fan is stronger than Cang Shan's father.

84
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:15,520
Unless you go in person,

85
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:16,900
if anyone else goes,

86
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,280
I'm afraid the outcome

87
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,390
will be the same.

88
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,000
Why have you suddenly come back?

89
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,560
Is something bothering you?

90
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,310
I don't know why,

91
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,630
but I have this inexplicable feeling of worry.

92
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,520
I told you,

93
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,740
as long as I'm here,

94
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,610
you don't need to worry about anything.

95
00:05:45,690 --> 00:05:47,360
Members of the Stone Clan suddenly died.

96
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,340
Cang Shan's father went missing,

97
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,390
and his mother came straight to you for help.

98
00:05:51,850 --> 00:05:54,090
I know you wouldn't stand by,

99
00:05:54,110 --> 00:05:56,500
but I feel a sense of danger.

100
00:05:56,530 --> 00:05:58,040
Cang Shan calls me Master.

101
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:59,330
It's natural that his mother

102
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,100
would come to me for help.

103
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:04,120
But now, you only have two stars left.

104
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,120
It's not so easy for me to lose a star.

105
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,390
I remember you once said

106
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:10,760
you didn't want to be cowardly

107
00:06:10,790 --> 00:06:12,610
because of the fear of danger.

108
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,770
But when it comes to me...

109
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,300
Bai Shuo.

110
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,020
The Contemplation Stone showed me another vision.

111
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,980
I saw a village

112
00:06:39,090 --> 00:06:40,960
full of jagged rocks.

113
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,680
If I'm not mistaken,

114
00:06:43,450 --> 00:06:44,770
the village you saw should be

115
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:46,250
the village of the Stone Clan.

116
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:47,920
Soon after Mrs. Cang came,

117
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,030
the Contemplation Stone was activated.

118
00:06:49,730 --> 00:06:51,200
I don't think it's a coincidence.

119
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,600
The kindness in Ning'an City,

120
00:06:52,659 --> 00:06:54,070
the killing in the Outlanders' City,

121
00:06:54,090 --> 00:06:56,430
and the love in Jingyou Mountain have all seen bloodshed.

122
00:06:56,460 --> 00:06:58,470
What remains are greed and hate.

123
00:06:58,990 --> 00:07:00,760
Both of them sound ominous.

124
00:07:00,910 --> 00:07:02,000
I'll go

125
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:02,920
to the Stone Clan.

126
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:04,010
You stay at the Unbridled Pavilion.

127
00:07:04,090 --> 00:07:06,860
I'm no longer the weak Bai Shuo I once was.

128
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,510
I can go with you.

129
00:07:08,930 --> 00:07:10,570
You cannot afford to lose another star.

130
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,990
Though you have power now,

131
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:14,150
the Contemplation Stone won't protect you anymore.

132
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:14,920
If anything happens...

133
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,870
Since it's an "if,"

134
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,640
it's beyond our control.

135
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,270
I can't hide forever,

136
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:22,310
never seeing anyone or doing anything.

137
00:07:22,790 --> 00:07:24,550
I'm not the type to run away.

138
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:29,860
Besides, the more Contemplations I collect,

139
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:31,600
the more power I will have.

140
00:07:32,150 --> 00:07:33,560
As long as I'm powerful enough,

141
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,070
I'll be my own shield,

142
00:07:35,220 --> 00:07:36,330
just like you.

143
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:37,810
As the Demon King of the Polar Region,

144
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,440
when did you ever need others' protection?

145
00:07:41,490 --> 00:07:43,220
I can't out-argue you anymore.

146
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:49,550
Master.

147
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,480
Bai Shuo.

148
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,890
I've made up my mind.

149
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,130
I'll handle my clan's trouble myself.

150
00:07:54,150 --> 00:07:55,030
Once it's resolved,

151
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,060
I'll reunite with you.

152
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:58,640
The next Contemplation

153
00:07:58,870 --> 00:07:59,920
is in the Stone Clan.

154
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:06,200
[Stone Clan, Demon Race]

155
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,230
Bai Shuo,

156
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:34,419
take a closer look.

157
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,090
Is the scene you saw from here?

158
00:08:36,730 --> 00:08:37,610
Yes.

159
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,220
So something big

160
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,610
is going to happen to the Stone Clan, right?

161
00:08:40,630 --> 00:08:42,480
The vision only showed this place.

162
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:44,510
Nothing terrifying has appeared yet.

163
00:08:44,530 --> 00:08:46,060
Don't panic.

164
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:48,150
What are you talking about?

165
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,240
What vision?

166
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,320
What is going to happen?

167
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:52,070
Mother, stop asking.

168
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:53,400
It's hard to explain.

169
00:08:53,430 --> 00:08:55,000
Since I've come to the Stone Clan,

170
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,000
I'm going to find out

171
00:08:57,330 --> 00:09:00,260
who's behind all these murders.

172
00:09:03,330 --> 00:09:04,540
Here we are.

173
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:10,980
Master Fan, Ms. Bai.

174
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,540
This place is not as good as the Unbridled Pavilion,

175
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,970
so you'll have to make do.

176
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,430
I'll go clean your rooms now.

177
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:18,490
Thank you, Mrs. Cang.

178
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:26,650
Cang Shan?

179
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,280
Shi Lei?

180
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:32,890
You've been gone for years.

181
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,270
You're finally back.

182
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:35,850
Have you learned that

183
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,050
[Shi Lei, Demon Race, Stone Clan]

184
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,010
something's happened in the clan?

185
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,520
I came back too late.

186
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:41,570
It's not too late.

187
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:42,710
What matters is you're back.

188
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,300
Master.

189
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,970
This is my best friend, Shi Lei.

190
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:47,690
This is the Master of Bright Moon Palace.

191
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,120
This is Ms. Bai, a human.

192
00:09:49,940 --> 00:09:50,610
Master...

193
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:52,320
Master of Bright Moon?

194
00:09:52,570 --> 00:09:53,330
Your mother said

195
00:09:53,350 --> 00:09:54,540
you work for Bright Moon Palace.

196
00:09:55,250 --> 00:09:56,250
That's actually true.

197
00:09:56,410 --> 00:09:58,230
Master and Ms. Bai are here to help us.

198
00:09:59,530 --> 00:10:00,370
Thank you, Master.

199
00:10:00,450 --> 00:10:01,480
Thank you, Ms. Bai.

200
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,020
You're our guests.

201
00:10:03,050 --> 00:10:04,290
We should treat you with hospitality.

202
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,790
But right now,

203
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,320
the Stone Clan…

204
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,000
We understand.

205
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:10,980
Time is tight.

206
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:12,080
Please tell Mrs. Cang to take us

207
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:14,120
to see the bodies of the victims first.

208
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:15,870
No need to trouble Mrs. Cang.

209
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:16,930
I know where they are.

210
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,800
I'll take you there.

211
00:10:25,010 --> 00:10:25,890
Master Fan.

212
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:26,870
Ms. Bai.

213
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:29,720
These are the bodies of the three murdered elders.

214
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:33,940
I'm fine.

215
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,960
Cang Shan,

216
00:10:36,980 --> 00:10:39,250
examine the cause of death and the wounds on their bodies.

217
00:10:52,330 --> 00:10:53,830
This one's bones are completely shattered.

218
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,310
This one too.

219
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:13,360
Master,

220
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,580
they weren't killed in one strike.

221
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:17,010
The murderer

222
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,630
shattered their bones first,

223
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:19,690
then tortured them to death.

224
00:11:21,110 --> 00:11:23,850
It looks like the work of a vengeful enemy.

225
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:26,130
The Stone Clan has been living in the mountains for many years.

226
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,300
We don't have any enemies.

227
00:11:27,380 --> 00:11:29,160
If it's not an enemy from another clan,

228
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,640
have you considered that the killer

229
00:11:30,660 --> 00:11:32,160
might be from within the Stone Clan?

230
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:33,070
Impossible.

231
00:11:33,090 --> 00:11:34,600
People here live in harmony.

232
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:35,650
There has never been any conflict.

233
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:37,770
No one would commit such a brutal act.

234
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:39,900
Not wanting to believe it doesn't mean it's impossible.

235
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:42,160
Before everything is clear,

236
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:45,040
everyone is a suspect.

237
00:12:08,970 --> 00:12:09,750
In Ning'an City,

238
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:11,100
the Outlanders' City,  and Jingyou Mountain,

239
00:12:11,130 --> 00:12:13,440
Young Lord saved and helped you again and again.

240
00:12:13,460 --> 00:12:14,460
When the Fox Clan's mission failed,

241
00:12:14,510 --> 00:12:15,950
she took the blame for you.

242
00:12:15,970 --> 00:12:17,770
Without the demonic flower armor protecting her,

243
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,050
the punishment

244
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:21,190
made her suffer far worse than before.

245
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,550
It's not because you're so great

246
00:12:22,570 --> 00:12:24,620
but because Young Lord has suffered too much since childhood

247
00:12:24,650 --> 00:12:26,050
that she treasures the little warmth

248
00:12:26,070 --> 00:12:28,140
you unknowingly gave her.

249
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:59,030
It's you.

250
00:12:59,050 --> 00:13:00,220
How do you feel?

251
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,150
What did you make me eat?

252
00:13:11,170 --> 00:13:12,900
Medicine for healing and pain relief.

253
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:15,100
It's a pill from Lanling?

254
00:13:15,850 --> 00:13:16,920
I'll take you out first.

255
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,990
If Grand Master finds out,

256
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:22,480
do you know the consequences?

257
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:24,020
No matter what the consequences are,

258
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,600
I'll take you out first.

259
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,960
Have you thought this through?

260
00:13:28,310 --> 00:13:29,100
If you save me,

261
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:32,090
you might be tortured by Grand Master until you're in pieces.

262
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:34,650
How can I hide behind you while you take the punishment

263
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,510
for the failed mission?

264
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:39,500
You've changed.

265
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:42,320
The world is full of uncertainties.

266
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:43,730
Whether things change or stay the same,

267
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:45,830
I'm just doing what I'm supposed to do.

268
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:49,220
But I don't understand one thing.

269
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:51,320
He treats you like this, making you suffer so much.

270
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:53,940
Why are you still so loyal to him,

271
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,550
still willing to risk your life for him?

272
00:13:58,000 --> 00:13:59,360
Those who gave birth to you

273
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,720
despised you for being weak and sick

274
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:04,030
and abandoned you in the wilderness.

275
00:14:04,410 --> 00:14:06,140
I pitied you,

276
00:14:06,170 --> 00:14:09,320
brought you back to Cold Spring Palace, and raised you.

277
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,640
You were born useless,

278
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,270
unable to transform

279
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,550
or cultivate.

280
00:14:15,950 --> 00:14:18,430
It was also me who put in so much effort

281
00:14:18,450 --> 00:14:21,100
to make you who you are today.

282
00:14:39,950 --> 00:14:43,290
♫Across thousands of miles♫

283
00:14:43,730 --> 00:14:45,400
