00:28:20,170 --> 00:28:21,760
Those two girls…

595
00:28:22,410 --> 00:28:24,240
Who are they?

596
00:28:25,120 --> 00:28:32,250
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

597
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:27,480
The dagger...

598
00:28:29,230 --> 00:28:30,580
Two girls...

599
00:28:32,900 --> 00:28:37,750
♫I'm your wanderer♫

600
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,480
Fu Ling,

601
00:28:34,730 --> 00:28:36,300
