734
00:35:10,410 --> 00:35:11,260
By the way,

735
00:35:11,290 --> 00:35:12,690
on the day the Baize Clan was wiped out,

736
00:35:12,710 --> 00:35:14,100
how did you survive?

737
00:35:15,650 --> 00:35:16,650
It was Grandfather.

738
00:35:18,730 --> 00:35:20,290
