742
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,670
You did that to avenge the Baize Clan,

743
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:25,320
didn't you?

744
00:35:27,030 --> 00:35:27,880
No, it wasn't me.

745
00:35:29,620 --> 00:35:30,450
Why?

746
00:35:31,090 --> 00:35:33,470
You're the Master of Bright Moon, the strongest demon in the world.

747
00:35:33,570 --> 00:35:35,260
Why didn't you avenge them?

748
00:35:35,290 --> 00:35:36,960
I went to the Tiger Clan to seek revenge.

749
00:35:37,490 --> 00:35:39,300
I also went there to look for you.

750
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:41,380
