00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,230
Then why didn't you tell the truth

843
00:38:24,230 --> 00:38:25,320
when the Tiger Clan came

844
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:28,730
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

845
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:26,410
looking for the purple-eyed boy?

846
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,320
And why didn't Grandfather…

847
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:28,190
Because Grandfather and the rest of the clan

848
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,710
had already made their choice.

849
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:32,590
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

850
00:38:31,660 --> 00:38:33,040
What could I do?

851
00:38:33,070 --> 00:38:35,390
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

852
00:38:35,850 --> 00:38:37,450
♫Time after time♫

853
00:38:38,210 --> 00:38:44,400
♫Oh, melancholy♫

854
00:39:09,890 --> 00:39:10,690
Fan Yue!

855
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:29,930
You don't need to say anything.

856
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:32,710
Calm down first.

857
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:40,720
So, I'm the purple-eyed boy.

858
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:44,490
The one the Tiger Clan wanted to capture back then was me.

859
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:47,930
♫The person standing far away♫

860
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:49,840
How could that be?

861
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:51,310
♫Don't be afraid♫

862
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,230
Then Grandfather

863
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:52,920
and the Baize Clan…

864
00:39:51,650 --> 00:39:56,370
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

865
00:39:52,950 --> 00:39:54,460
Grandfather and the clan stayed silent

866
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:56,040
in order to protect me.

867
00:39:56,250 --> 00:39:58,160
They all chose to sacrifice Qi Feng.

868
00:39:57,210 --> 00:40:03,600
♫Walk towards me♫

869
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:00,710
Bai Shuo,

870
00:40:02,510 --> 00:40:03,670
who am I really?

871
00:40:04,130 --> 00:40:06,240
What does being the purple-eyed boy mean?

872
00:40:05,530 --> 00:40:08,280
♫My heart feels so...♫

873
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:09,110
Why did everyone sacrifice themselves for me?

874
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:14,540
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

875
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:10,940
Everything I have now

876
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:13,000
was bought with Qi Feng's suffering

877
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:13,760
and pain.

878
00:40:16,540 --> 00:40:20,430
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

879
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:21,530
Don't put all the blame on yourself.

880
00:40:22,950 --> 00:40:24,470
No matter who you are,

881
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:27,390
♫You are my distant call♫

882
00:40:25,100 --> 00:40:27,230
you were innocent back then.

883
00:40:27,570 --> 00:40:29,610
Do you remember what Grandfather told you

884
00:40:27,870 --> 00:40:32,340
♫You are my first and last♫

885
00:40:29,640 --> 00:40:30,730
before he passed away?

886
00:40:31,190 --> 00:40:32,920
He told you to live well.

887
00:40:33,070 --> 00:40:39,160
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

888
00:40:34,820 --> 00:40:36,090
One day,

889
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:38,020
you'll understand who you are.

890
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:41,580
You can't let Qi Feng's sudden return

891
00:40:39,580 --> 00:40:42,470
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

892
00:40:41,600 --> 00:40:43,520
erase all the pain you've endured

893
00:40:42,950 --> 00:40:47,000
♫Let's never let go♫

894
00:40:43,550 --> 00:40:45,240
and all the effort you've made.

895
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,270
What we need to do now

896
00:40:48,290 --> 00:40:50,570
is uncover the truth behind everything,

897
00:40:50,740 --> 00:40:52,490
protect those who need protecting,

898
00:40:52,970 --> 00:40:54,260
and keep living.

899
00:40:54,620 --> 00:40:56,080
That's what Grandfather

900
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,510
would want to see the most.

901
00:41:05,100 --> 00:41:10,090
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

902
00:41:12,540 --> 00:41:16,530
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

903
00:41:17,120 --> 00:41:22,090
♫You are my determined way home♫

904
00:41:21,630 --> 00:41:23,420
She came to Cold Spring Palace ten years ago.

905
00:41:23,450 --> 00:41:24,860
She knows my parents

906
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,500
and the Chong family's motto.

907
00:41:27,300 --> 00:41:28,610
More importantly,

908
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:30,770
she has memories of Bai Shuo's dagger.

909
00:41:31,260 --> 00:41:32,180
Could it be…

910
00:41:32,640 --> 00:41:35,150
she's Bai Xi, who went missing ten years ago?

911
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:38,870
Follow the way of heaven as the way.

912
00:41:39,350 --> 00:41:40,540
Practice goodness,

913
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:42,840
caution,

914
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,920
and harmony.

915
00:41:48,170 --> 00:41:49,920
If Fu Ling really is Bai Xi,

916
00:41:49,950 --> 00:41:51,160
after she killed Uncle Bai

917
00:41:51,180 --> 00:41:52,710
and has repeatedly tried to kill Shuo,

918
00:41:53,200 --> 00:41:55,430
how could she possibly face the truth?

919
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,850
And for Shuo,

920
00:41:58,220 --> 00:42:00,510
if she learns that the sister she's been missing every day

921
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:02,570
is actually the person she hates most,

922
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:04,690
how will she accept it?

923
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,810
But Bai Xi was a human,

924
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,220
while Fu Ling is a demon.

925
00:42:08,430 --> 00:42:09,840
Why is that?

926
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:13,290
Fu Ling's identity isn't fully confirmed yet.

927
00:42:13,490 --> 00:42:14,760
Telling Master now

928
00:42:14,790 --> 00:42:15,910
might be too soon.

929
00:42:17,010 --> 00:42:18,710
I hope I'm wrong.

930
00:42:20,010 --> 00:42:21,810
A truth so cruel

931
00:42:22,450 --> 00:42:24,590
might as well remain a mystery forever.

932
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:31,630
Sect Leader,

933
00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:33,030
you want to see me?

934
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,030
I haven't received

935
00:42:36,030 --> 00:42:37,880
any word from Chong Zhao in some time.

936
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:40,110
I wonder how things are going on his side.

937
00:42:40,510 --> 00:42:43,250
The last time you saw that evil insect in Ning'an City,

938
00:42:43,550 --> 00:42:45,110
it was almost fully grown.

939
00:42:45,770 --> 00:42:47,250
By now, it's probably

940
00:42:47,270 --> 00:42:49,010
already fully grown.

941
00:42:49,080 --> 00:42:50,520
I've already notified other Eternal sects.

942
00:42:50,540 --> 00:42:53,310
Their disciples have strengthened daily patrols and inspections.

943
00:42:53,340 --> 00:42:55,080
No trace of the evil insect has been found.

944
00:42:55,280 --> 00:42:56,780
I wonder what that old dragon from Cold Spring Palace

945
00:42:56,810 --> 00:42:58,800
intends to do with the evil insect.

946
00:42:58,830 --> 00:43:02,630
The evil insect was created by Chen Ye from Cold Spring Palace.

947
00:43:02,650 --> 00:43:05,810
It's said that he's highly skilled in weaponry and poison-making.

948
00:43:06,550 --> 00:43:07,880
I'm worried...

949
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:09,920
Sect Leader, are you worried

950
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:11,190
that once the evil insect is unleashed,

951
00:43:11,210 --> 00:43:11,960
its harm

952
00:43:11,990 --> 00:43:13,820
may rival the Nether Poison from back then?

953
00:43:14,370 --> 00:43:16,570
I hope I'm overthinking it.

954
00:43:20,710 --> 00:43:22,670
May what I fear

955
00:43:22,690 --> 00:43:24,810
never come to pass.

956
00:43:37,710 --> 00:43:38,500
Come in.

957
00:43:43,510 --> 00:43:44,530
You are…

958
00:43:44,550 --> 00:43:45,430
Bai Shuo.

959
00:43:45,460 --> 00:43:46,460
You're injured.

960
00:43:46,510 --> 00:43:47,550
I've brought some pills

961
00:43:47,550 --> 00:43:48,550
specifically for you.

962
00:43:49,940 --> 00:43:51,310
You're a physician?

963
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:52,840
I'm Fan Yue's friend,

964
00:43:53,070 --> 00:43:54,230
and I know a little about medicine.

965
00:43:54,600 --> 00:43:55,640
These pills

966
00:43:55,880 --> 00:43:57,360
will help with your injuries.

967
00:43:57,800 --> 00:43:59,760
That's very thoughtful of you. Thank you.

968
00:43:59,880 --> 00:44:02,010
While you were unconscious, I examined your injuries.

969
00:44:02,400 --> 00:44:04,400
Your recent wounds are all external

970
00:44:04,400 --> 00:44:05,820
and will heal quickly.

971
00:44:05,850 --> 00:44:07,720
As for your legs,

972
00:44:08,210 --> 00:44:09,920
I don't have a way to treat them right now.

973
00:44:09,950 --> 00:44:10,950
I know.

974
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,510
My spiritual veins are all severed.

975
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:13,620
No medicine can help.

976
00:44:14,150 --> 00:44:15,670
That's what the previous physicians said too.

977
00:44:16,030 --> 00:44:16,830
It's fine.

978
00:44:16,900 --> 00:44:18,090
I'm used to it.

979
00:44:18,120 --> 00:44:19,330
Thank you for your concern.

980
00:44:20,560 --> 00:44:22,290
Since you're Yue's friend,

981
00:44:22,320 --> 00:44:23,720
then you're also my friend.

982
00:44:25,780 --> 00:44:27,010
I don't have much to give,

983
00:44:27,040 --> 00:44:28,330
just a few small handmade things.

984
00:44:28,560 --> 00:44:30,710
I made this bamboo dragonfly myself.

985
00:44:30,840 --> 00:44:32,570
I'd like to give it to you as a thank-you gift.

986
00:44:36,780 --> 00:44:39,020
It's not as precious as these pills,

987
00:44:39,130 --> 00:44:40,360
but it's a token of my appreciation.

988
00:44:40,960 --> 00:44:42,390
It looks delicate.

989
00:44:42,830 --> 00:44:44,170
I'm glad you don't find it too simple.

990
00:44:46,920 --> 00:44:48,250
Is Yue okay?
